title: Tidy Fundamental Financial Data from SECs EDGAR API
text: tidyedgar R package designed simplify acquiring transforming fundamental financial data EDGAR database. Leveraging official S.E.C. API, TidyEDGAR outputs data clean, ‘tidy’ format ideal financial analysis stock screening based fundamental data.

title: Tidy Fundamental Financial Data from SECs EDGAR API
text: Ease Use: Automates retrieval preprocessing financial data. Tidy Format: Structures data convenient format analysis. Comprehensive Coverage: Access data across U.S. public companies. Versatile Analysis: Suitable fundamental analysis stock screening.
